00元，再加上區議員的33,950及行會成員最新調整的酬金，合共達184,500元。"},{"pid":"d4ae675ca3cdabadeae4c795c23f1cd5a0c76987","tid":1751414,"uid":46746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"915d8c56e0a983ad8076f1edd7850b6ad7bca298","tid":1751414,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:18:45.000Z","msg":"另外<br />\n港共只係出賣咗保皇黨其中一個cap水點<br />\n但就一次過消咗5個月積落嘅民氣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:36:16.000Z","msg":"唔會咁易完 區議會只係階段性勝利"},{"pid":"269412f7b9dfec51b42fd9522d55b530f7f6c589","tid":1751414,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1ebd84ca75ed0f40ac084efe4514b31eea8dda89","tid":1751414,"uid":324363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c02fa69cf5315872739f05d0ff21171efc78c4f2","tid":1751414,"uid":175930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0bed669547532579198f736bf1a244c05947cfe","tid":1751414,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:15:25.000Z","msg":"下年立法會大Q獲<br />\n配到仆街"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:31:02.000Z","msg":"咁我地都可以學配嘅姐 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n經過呢幾個月<br />\n我已經覺得冇嘢不可能"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:35:06.000Z","msg":"我地點會配到&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n依加講緊無撞區無鬼就唔洗配<br />\n反而係政黨要明白個區選民嘅政治取態"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:36:55.000Z","msg":"其實最好就用一張名單入4 5 個<br />\n谷晒d 票去同一個倉到<br />\n咁7:3 比就輸梗<br />\n<br />\n不過邊個行頭邊個行尾<br />\n咁大利益 販民實唔制"},{"pid":"693d6aba6ae2fece56eebcb6e34a1cd800a5338e","tid":1751414,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T17:38:25.000Z","msg":"唔算<br />\n因為登記日係72截止<br />\n好多人都係721 831之後先覺醒<br />\n呢班721前沉默的大多數未必有登記做選民<br />\n相反建制基本上動員哂所以力量去投票(未fc 要睇返過往同今界建制的票數有幾大分別)"},{"pid":"4a25fb38677685c37f25e841323099e482806be5","tid":1751414,"uid":318300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"269412f7b9dfec51b42fd9522d55b530f7f6c589","tid":1751414,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1ebd84